#: ../../source/unit/co2l.rst:3 3adf2df215f642fda492b5de58211f2c
msgid "CO2L Unit"
msgstr "CO2L Unit"

#: ../../source/unit/co2l.rst:7 d87c85c8ec4a490b9935850c0c85c1e2
#, python-format
msgid ""
"UNIT CO2L is a digital air CO2 concentration detection unit with a "
"single-measurement low-power mode, built-in Sensirion's SCD41 sensor and "
"power buck circuitry, and I2C communication. The unit is suitable for the"
" measurement of air ambient conditions with a typical accuracy of ± (40 "
"ppm + 5 % reading) for CO2 measurements over a measuring range of 400 ppm"
" – 5000 ppm while measuring ambient temperature and humidity."
msgstr ""
"UNIT CO2L 是一款数字空气 CO2 浓度检测 Unit，支持单次测量低功耗模式，内置 Sensirion 的 SCD41 "
"传感器和降压电源电路，并通过 I2C 通信。该 Unit 适用于空气环境条件测量，CO2 测量范围为 400 ppm – 5000 "
"ppm，在同时测量环境温度和湿度的情况下，CO2 测量的典型精度为 ±（40 ppm + 5 % 读数）。"

